<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[الاستعداد]</span>: استعدَّ للشيء،<span class="c5"> من العُدَّة:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إذا تهيأ له.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
